The paper deals with the concept of formal concept analysis, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves quantitative analysis of data sets, which is a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG). The use of implication bases is related to database theory (cs.DB) and the study of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS). Finally, the paper discusses the representation of knowledge from data sets, which is a topic in information retrieval (cs.IR).
